10:1](../../../bib/apo/wis010.htm#001.md)<span
id="iv.iii.xii.v-p3.1"></span> where Adam is called <span
class="Greek"><span id="iv.iii.xii.v-p3.2"></span>πρωτοπλαστος</span>.
